\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\series bold
Component Skills:
\series default
 Medicine, Science, Computer
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection*
Create 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The Create Skill describes the Luminous' ability to create new things or
 express inner truths.
 It is used to sew clothing, create paintings, write poems, build a tent
 in the wilderness, perform magical rituals, and speak convincingly to a
 large audience.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\series bold

\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

