Crafts, Expression, Survival
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection*
Connect 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The Connect skill describes the Luminous' force of personality and ability
 to reach out to others.
 It is used to convince people to your side, make prepared speeches, navigate
 bureaucracy, reach out to another in need, and prove your trustworthiness
 to those suspicious of you.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\series bold

\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

Sample Actions:
\series default
 Speak to a crowd (Power + Connect), Navigate bureaucracy (Resistance +
 Connect), Make an impassioned plea (Power + Connect)
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\series bold
Component Skills:
\series default
 Persuasion, Politics, Streetwise
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection*
Shade
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The Shade skill describes the Luminous' skill at hiding their intent and
 acting secretively.
 It is used to hide yourself physically, lie to another, hide your true
 emotions, pickpocket items off another, pick open a door, and convey hidden
 meaning in what you say.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\series bold

\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

Sample Actions:
\series default
 Follow someone secretly (Finesse + Shade), Conceal your emotions (Resistance
 + Shade), Disguise yourself (Finesse + Shade)
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\series bold
Component Skills:
\series default
 Stealth, Subterfuge, Larceny
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection*
Resonate
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The Resonate skill describes the Luminous' ability to understand others
 and the world around you in intuitive ways.
 It is used to understand others, detect lies and concealed intentions,
 sympathize with another's pain, understand hidden and occult meanings,
 handle animals, and fit into a crowd.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\series bold

\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

Sample Actions:
\series default
 Detect a lie (Finesse + Resonate), Fit into a crowd (Power + Resonate),
